Articles.Content:
Hi there

I stumbled across Planet Factory, a mod which adds a few more planets to KSP. The problem is I have no idea what is going on with the mod, the download links are all gone yet I'm able to find a link to the "source code" from github. it is 48mb in size so I assumed this was the mod itself.

When adding it I can see it loading the resources in the loader when you start the game up but nothing changes I don't see any new planets.

Was this mod in violation of terms or something? Why is it so hard to track down, if someone has a link to the working mod please share it with me I"m quite interested in it. Thanks.
